(2, 'Industry', 'The industry is the production of goods or related services within an economy. The major source of revenue of a group or company is the indicator of its relevant industry. When a large group has multiple sources of revenue generation, it is considered to be working in different industries.', 0, '1538464763.jpg', 'Industry', '0', 'Y', '2018-10-03 02:49:23', '2018-10-03 02:49:23'),
