(5, 'Society', 'A society is a group of individuals involved in the persistent social interaction, or a large social group sharing the same geographical or social territory, typically subject to the same political authority and dominant cultural expectations', 0, '1538465119.jpg', 'Society', '0', 'Y', '2018-10-03 02:55:19', '2018-10-03 02:55:19'),
(6, 'Art', 'Art is a diverse range of human activities in creating visual, auditory or performing artefacts (artworks), expressing the author\'s imaginative, conceptual idea, or technical skill, intended to be appreciated for their beauty or emotional power.', 1, '1538465243.jpg', 'Art', '0', 'Y', '2018-10-03 02:57:23', '2018-10-03 02:57:23'),
(7, 'Book excerpts', 'When the word is used as a verb, excerpt means to take a portion out, usually from a play, book, article, song, or other written work. And the part that is taken out also is called an excerpt, but it is a noun, that is, a thing. An excerpt is something you excerpt, or pluck out, from a larger piece.', 1, '1538465427.jpg', 'Book-excerpts', '0', 'Y', '2018-10-03 03:00:27', '2018-10-03 03:00:27'),
