(12, 'Gaming', 'Gaming is the act of playing games, as in: Legalized gambling, playing games of chance for money, often referred to in law as \"gaming\".', 1, '1538468778.jpg', 'Gaming', '0', 'Y', '2018-10-03 03:56:18', '2018-10-03 03:56:18'),
