(21, 'True crime', 'True crime is a non-fiction literary and film genre in which the author examines an actual crime and details the actions of real people. ... Although the genre examines real historical events, true crime TV series typically use reenactments to help draw in viewers.', 1, '1538471172.jpeg', 'True-crime', '0', 'Y', '2018-10-03 04:36:12', '2018-10-03 04:36:12'),
